  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of Helena Nightshade </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the mystery of the Eternal Lunar Eclipse </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through 1930s Southern Europe </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35 chapters with 1-3 sub scenes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >29 subgames relating to the story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 special chapters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Wallpapers</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in 1930s Southern Europe, where technology has eclipsed magic, an estranged group of Moon Worshippers known as the Anaxagori resurfaces with an ominous prophecy: an eternal lunar eclipse. Dismissed by the public as antiquated mystics, the Anaxagori's warnings contrast sharply with the populace's enthusiasm for what is hailed as a historic celestial event. Fresh from an archaeological expedition, Helena Nightshade only learns of the eclipse's significance upon arriving in Istanbul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.poster.avif?t=1730783087\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.webm?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.mp4?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Initially drawn by the thrill of adventure, Helena soon discovers that fate has a hand in her involvement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.poster.avif?t=1730783087\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.webm?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.mp4?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this point-and-click hidden object adventure game, you will guide Helena as she pieces together clues in her journal, discovers hidden objects throughout her journey, and solves a variety of puzzles and minigames!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore richly detailed scenes, interact with intriguing characters, become friends with a certain avian, and aid the right forces to prevent the cataclysmic tragedy!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in 1930s Southern Europe, where technology has eclipsed magic, an estranged group of Moon Worshippers known as the Anaxagori resurfaces with an ominous prophecy: an eternal lunar eclipse. Dismissed by the public as antiquated mystics, the Anaxagori's warnings contrast sharply with the populace's enthusiasm for what is hailed as a historic celestial event. Fresh from an archaeological expedition, Helena Nightshade only learns of the eclipse's significance upon arriving in Istanbul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.poster.avif?t=1730783087\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.webm?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/25c2494fba1e3b89db0d2105bc52b738.mp4?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Initially drawn by the thrill of adventure, Helena soon discovers that fate has a hand in her involvement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.poster.avif?t=1730783087\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.webm?t=1730783087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/0dd833c4abe5da9c6eb122c72429be19.mp4?t=1730783087